title: Raanan Hershberg
itunes:title: Raanan Hershberg
description:
Stand up comedian and host of the JOE AND RAANAN TALK MOVIES podcast Raanan Hershberg is on the show and it's a film lover's spectacular. Whitney has non stop hot takes, Raanan hates GOOD WILL HUNTING, and they discuss alleged munchkin molestation on the set of THE WIZARD OF OZ.  Raanan also has Whitney's favorite Covid and Me Too joke. Plus, the GOOD FOR YOU team opens the show with another round of impressions. Watch out SNL.
